alan Pengarah Imigresen negeri Zulhilmi Zulkifli ketika mengesahkan perkara itu berkata suspek kini direman selama tujuh hari dan PATI berkenaan kini ditahan pihaknya.\u003C\/p\u003E  \u003Cp align=\"justify\"\u003EKatanya, suspek yang dipercayai sudah empat kali melakukan aktiviti penyeludupan manusia sebelum ini akan disiasat mengikut Seksyen 26K(2) Akta Anti-Pemerdagangan Orang dan Anti Penyeludupan Migran 2007. –myMetro\u003C\/p\u003E  "},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/feeds\/6225570621356645895\/comments\/default","title":"Post Comments"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/2014\/12\/polis-ditahan-cuba-seludup-manusia.html#comment-form","title":"0 Comments"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5125969139163369716\/posts\/default\/6225570621356645895"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5125969139163369716\/posts\/default\/6225570621356645895"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/2014\/12\/polis-ditahan-cuba-seludup-manusia.html","title":"POLIS DITAHAN CUBA SELUDUP MANUSIA"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"Malaya Mania"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/13745450945166190393"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"32","height":"32","src":"http:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-T6cNx0o4Wtg\/VFrUmpLFJdI\/AAAAAAAABmk\/7ST-kff-_uE\/s1600\/*"}}],"media$thumbnail":{"xmlns$media":"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/","url":"http:\/\/lh5.ggpht.com\/-U8zUAE2CJ4g\/VIURLnbB9II\/AAAAAAAAB0A\/YkeKB63D-H4\/s72-c\/seludup%252520orang_thumb%25255B18%25255D.jpg?imgmax=800","height":"72","width":"72"},"thr$total":{"$t":"0"}},{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5125969139163369716.post-1798313989768766638"},"published":{"$t":"2014-12-02T16:36:00.001+08:00"},"updated"