at kuih kerana masalah kesihatan berikutan terdapat ketumbuhan di dalam rahim,” katanya.\u003C\/p\u003E  \u003Cp align=\"justify\"\u003EMenurutnya, dia kini mendapatkan rawatan susulan di Hospital Sultanah Nur Zahirah, di sini, berikutan penyakit dialaminya itu.\u003C\/p\u003E  \u003Cp align=\"justify\"\u003EKatanya, dia dan bapanya berharap untuk mendapatkan bantuan kaki palsu bagi memudahkan mereka bergerak dan menjalankan aktiviti harian.\u003C\/p\u003E  \u003Cp align=\"justify\"\u003EZila berkata, dengan adanya kaki palsu mungkin lebih memudahkan pergerakan dia dan bapanya berikutan pergerakan hariannya terhad kerana menggunakan kerusi roda. –myMetro\u003C\/p\u003E  "},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/feeds\/7305884842440190940\/comments\/default","title":"Post Comments"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/2014\/11\/derita-tanggung-bersama.html#comment-form","title":"0 Comments"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5125969139163369716\/posts\/default\/7305884842440190940"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5125969139163369716\/posts\/default\/7305884842440190940"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/2014\/11\/derita-tanggung-bersama.html","title":"‘DERITA TANGGUNG BERSAMA…’"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"Malaya Mania"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/13745450945166190393"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"32","height":"32","src":"http:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-T6cNx0o4Wtg\/VFrUmpLFJdI\/AAAAAAAABmk\/7ST-kff-_uE\/s1600\/*"}}],"media$thumbnail":{"xmlns$media":"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/","url":"http:\/\/lh3.ggpht.com\/-eWYQGdVMJd4\/VHfQv9H4CYI\/AAAAAAAAByk\/f3VkhvV45kA\/s72-c\/derita_thumb%25255B6%25255D.jpg?imgmax=800","height