n cota di kepala serta menyimbah air panas ke badan mangsa.\u003C\/p\u003E  \u003Cp align=\"justify\"\u003EBiras mangsa, Rubiah Manaf, 57, berkata, kejadian itu di­sedari seorang saudara mangsa yang tinggal berdekatan selepas mendengar jeritan Wak Jamil mengerang kesakitan.\u003C\/p\u003E  \u003Cp align=\"justify\"\u003E“Sebaik membuka pintu rumah mangsa, saudara mangsa terkejut melihat keadaan Wak Jamil yang berlumuran darah, tidak bermaya dan cuba merangkak meminta pertolongan,” kata Rubiah ketika ditemui di rumahnya semalam. –Kosmo\u003C\/p\u003E  "},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/feeds\/2797810827683189130\/comments\/default","title":"Post Comments"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/2014\/11\/didera-menantu-perangai-hantu.html#comment-form","title":"0 Comments"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5125969139163369716\/posts\/default\/2797810827683189130"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5125969139163369716\/posts\/default\/2797810827683189130"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/malayamania.blogspot.com\/2014\/11\/didera-menantu-perangai-hantu.html","title":"DIDERA MENANTU PERANGAI HANTU"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"Malaya Mania"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/13745450945166190393"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"32","height":"32","src":"http:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-T6cNx0o4Wtg\/VFrUmpLFJdI\/AAAAAAAABmk\/7ST-kff-_uE\/s1600\/*"}}],"media$thumbnail":{"xmlns$media":"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/","url":"http:\/\/lh4.ggpht.com\/-I_sRgmGrppI\/VHfHmrKe6jI\/AAAAAAAAByM\/biIWbiPnwG8\/s72-c\/menantu%252520hantu_thumb%25255B6%25255D.jpg?imgmax=800","height":"72","width":"72"},"thr$total":{"$t":"0"}}]}});